title: Confidence
pageBody:
During this course you have acquired new competencies that will enable you to use the TCPR link system to increase the CPR quality and thereby improve the chance of survival for people suffering a cardiac arrest.

As a conclusion for this e-learning course, please complete the following survey to indicate your own perceived confidence levels.
